{"tid":1344153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要成立臨時政府，而唔係臨時立法會","createTime":"2019-07-21T20:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T10:01:28.000Z","uid":276020,"like":44,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2818e5a574ca28349718c5bc3a29ab34eb7d38f5","tid":1344153,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:44:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">臨時政府可以</span></span> 但臨時立法會係唔關事 <br />\n<br />\n臨時立法會要做嘅野係立法，討論議案，依家都冇議案要討論。最重要係，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你討論完要真係立法到先得架！</span></span> ，你講幾多野都好，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自己立個法，冇執法，冇人理，係冇用架！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港政府唔可信，完全失效，警黑合作，所以要有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">臨時政府</span></span>負責<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">處理社會事務</span></span>，例如 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">成立自衛隊</span></span>保護市民，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">成立對外宣傳組</span></span>，負責見記者，資訊流通等等。 咁就真係將依家既抗爭者connect，各展所長。"},{"pid":"2d3c5f9715375de853e1e113fcb531e95acc65ed","tid":1344153,"uid":276020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2818e5a574ca28349718c5bc3a29ab34eb7d38f5","tid":1344153,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:44:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">臨時政府可以</span></span> 但臨時立法會係唔關事 <br />\n<br />\n臨時立法會要做嘅野係立法，討論議案，依家都冇議案要討論。最重要係，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你討論完要真係立法到先得架！</span></span> ，你講幾多野都好，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自己立個法，冇執法，冇人理，係冇用架！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港政府唔可信，完全失效，警黑合作，所以要有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">臨時政府</span></span>負責<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">處理社會事務</span></span>，例如 <span style=\"font-size: x-larg